body: Welcome to PluginLearn! I am a brand new bukkit plugin developer, so you can come check out mah plugins! Sorry, but I'm VERY new, and I still don't know much about Java, but I have studied some Python and a little of Javascript, so I am excited to learn Java. Thanks for viewing mah page! See ya on Minecraft!
